title: ...LOST SURF SKATE CONTEST IN PORTA ALEGRE, BRAZIL
description: There's no better way to introduce the new surf inspired collection of ...LOST surf skates then to take it to the one of the longest snake runs in the world and put on a contest of surf-skate slashes! Porto Alegre, Brazil home of The Marinha, Skate Park with a snake run that's over 500ft long. and over 30 years old.
